snippet.title: Time To Cook | Toca Kitchen | Gameplay Trailer | @TocaBoca
snippet.description:
Never miss a new trailer ★ SUBSCRIBE ★ http://bit.ly/Subscribe_Now_TocaBoca

In Toca Kitchen, you get to cook for four hungry characters. Pick your ingredients from the fridge and prepare them in any way you like. Free exploratory play with food in a new way. Let's find out what their preferences are!

➤ Available on the App Store: http://bit.ly/get_tocakitchen_appstore
